thread.title: Christine
thread.title_full: Ocean County Veterinary Hospital reviewed by Christine

author: Christine
title: Christine
text: I called the office on Sunday about my cat vomiting and was able to get an appointment for the next day, which was great as it was not an emergency. The staff was efficient and caring. My cat was seen by Dr. Iaquinto who was also very caring. She examined my cat and asked many questions and suggested we try some easy fixes before taking a lot of expensive tests. I liked that as my cat seems healthy other than the vomiting. We followed all of her suggestions and thankfully they seem to be working.
